{"tid":1475623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"818一行出馬路，黑警已經可以大條道理出tear gas","createTime":"2019-08-15T14:13:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T14:26:33.000Z","uid":135274,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"32f08ae2757df5176e57efbb3e415ba2c15f82af","tid":1475623,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:13:52.000Z","msg":"叫人唔好帶gear既人，根本就係心存僥倖，覺得人數一多，黑警就唔夠膽亂黎。<br />\n<br />\n元朗民居可以放tear gas，黃大仙街坊屌狗可以出tear gas，深水埗燒街衣都可以出tear gas。<br />\n<br />\n點解你地仲可以天真嬌到以為，你地自己定性做「和理非」回合，黑警就唔會搞你？<br />\n<br />\n係呢個時候，仲對政權既武裝力量有任何幻想，就係傷害自己，而帶gear，只係保護自己既行為。"},{"pid":"b9aee203c4a63bcafaebecb34acecf2da0565a1a","tid":1475623,"uid":241244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:14:27.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b61d575399f4628c4f0457b57e21668eefa2f243","tid":1475623,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a987bf6fb7ea4d082bdfa50cb67f4503d6ce30f1","tid":1475623,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:15:25.000Z","msg":"老閪都帶，明明帶咗又唔會俾人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d70fdb29f250ee0d8662a739a095f249472203c0","tid":1475623,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:16:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a541b89fbc97383faf8487034933b02f2db7a635","tid":1475623,"uid":241458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:17:08.000Z","msg":"保護自己一定要帶gear <br />\n<br />\n818由維園合法集會坐返出去，今次要多人俾國際睇到，證明兩個月以來，香港人仲係堅持緊<br />\n唔好嚇走一家大細嘅人"},{"pid":"e140103b45b30ed23479ff87b382c2d62ea9644b","tid":1475623,"uid":295889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite